# DELETE in DB

### deleteOne()

```bash
db.collection.deleteOne(<filter>, <option>)
```
```bash
db.student.deleteOne( {name: "Farah"})
{ acknowledged: true, deletedCount: 1 }
```

<br>

### deleteMany()

```bash
db.collection.deleteMany(<filter>, <option>)

db.student.deleteOne({}) //to delete all documents in the collection
```
```bash
db.student.deleteOne( {city: "Mumbai"})
{ acknowledged: true, deletedCount: 2 }
```

<br>

### dropDatabase()

```bash
db.dropDatabase()
```

<br>

[Click here](https://www.mongodb.com/docs/manual/tutorial/remove-documents/) for more info.